snippet.title: H1Z1: Battle Royale | Launch Trailer | PS4
snippet.description: H1Z1: Battle Royale is a pure, fast-paced battle royale shooter re-imagined and built for console. Drop in to a massive map in search of weapons, ammo, vehicles and air drops to get a leg up on the competition and be the last one standing: https://play.st/H1Z1
